	* Makefile.am (dist-hook): Qualify target with $(srcdir)/ prefix.

2004-02-11  Jim Meyering  <jim@meyering.net>

	* tests/Makefile.am.in ($(srcdir)/Makefile.am): Use more portable
	$(srcdir)/../Makefile.am.in, rather than $<.
