	but is slightly cleaner.
	(prjoin): Hoist (tab ? tab : ' ') expression, to help the compiler.

	(empty_filler): Now const *.

	(make_blank): Remove; wasn't needed.  Remove all calls.
	(main): Don't set uni_blank.nfields; zero is fine.

